highlights.text: The Weeknd has the most spots on Top Songs Global. “Blinding Lights” is the highest at #47.
“Believer” by Imagine Dragons has been on Top Songs Global the longest, at 256 weeks straight.
“Toma Toma Vapo Vapo” by Zé Felipe and Mc Danny is the biggest gainer on Top Songs Global, up 47 spots at #104.
“Christmas Tree” by V is the highest new entry on Top Songs Global at #100.
